short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Go back to Meet tab, Mute and Unmute yourself from anywhere on Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
So you are in a middle of your important meeting but you visited another chrome tab/window to check something more important, and now you cannot find your way back to the Google Meet tab?
This extension allows you to do the following:
1. Mute/Unmute microphone from anywhere on Chrome
2. Go back to the Google Meet tab hosting your meeting from tab/window

Update: Added keyboard shortcuts for the above actions. Find Meet It in the Keyboard shortcuts menu from the chrome://extensions page.
